    <title>JavaScript 常用代码段</title>
    <url>/2019/10/07/JavaScript-Skills/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>JavaScript 编写中可能用到的技巧，熟练运用后说不定会有事半功倍的效果</p>
<span id="more"></span>

<h2 id="Quick-Console-log"><a href="#Quick-Console-log" class="headerlink" title="Quick Console.log"></a>Quick Console.log</h2><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span><span class="javascript"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">    <span class="keyword">let</span> c = <span class="built_in">console</span>.log.bind(<span class="built_in">document</span>)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">    <span class="keyword">let</span> info = <span class="built_in">console</span>.info.bind(<span class="built_in">document</span>)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">    c(<span class="string">&quot;This is JavaScript&quot;</span>)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">    c(<span class="literal">true</span>)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">    c(<span class="number">12345</span>)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">    info(<span class="string">&quot;This is JavaScript&quot;</span>)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">    info(<span class="literal">true</span>)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">    info(<span class="number">12345</span>)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript"></span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<blockquote>
<p>更加简短的 console.log() 或者是 console.info() </p>
</blockquote>
<h2 id="箭头函数"><a href="#箭头函数" class="headerlink" title="箭头函数"></a>箭头函数</h2><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span><span class="javascript"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">    <span class="function"><span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="title">print1</span>(<span class="params"></span>) </span>&#123;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">        <span class="built_in">console</span>.log(<span class="string">&quot;Hello World&quot;</span>)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">    &#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">    <span class="keyword">let</span> print2 = <span class="function">() =&gt;</span> &#123;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">        <span class="built_in">console</span>.log(<span class="string">&quot;Hello World&quot;</span>)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">    &#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">    <span class="function"><span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="title">sum</span>(<span class="params">x, y</span>) </span>&#123;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">        <span class="keyword">return</span> x + y</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">    &#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">    <span class="keyword">let</span> sum2 = <span class="function">(<span class="params">x, y</span>) =&gt;</span> &#123;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">        <span class="keyword">return</span> x + y</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">    &#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript"></span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<blockquote>
<p>通过箭头函数有效减少代码量，熟悉后更易阅读</p>
</blockquote>
<h2 id="Spread-Operator"><a href="#Spread-Operator" class="headerlink" title="Spread Operator"></a>Spread Operator</h2><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span><span class="javascript"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">    <span class="comment">// Array connection</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">    <span class="keyword">let</span> num1 = [<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">3</span>]</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">    <span class="keyword">let</span> num2 = [<span class="number">4</span>, <span class="number">5</span>, <span class="number">6</span>]</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">    <span class="keyword">let</span> concat = [...num1, ...num2]                 <span class="comment">// [1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6]</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">    <span class="built_in">console</span>.log(concat)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">    <span class="comment">// Copying An Array</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">    <span class="keyword">let</span> alpha = [<span class="string">&#x27;a&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;b&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;c&#x27;</span>]</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">    <span class="keyword">let</span> copy = [...alpha]                           <span class="comment">// [&#x27;a&#x27;,&#x27;b&#x27;,&#x27;c&#x27;]</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">    <span class="built_in">console</span>.log(copy)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">    <span class="comment">// Array literals</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">    <span class="keyword">let</span> data = [<span class="number">100</span>, <span class="number">200</span>]</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">    <span class="keyword">let</span> literal = [...data, <span class="number">300</span>, <span class="number">400</span>, <span class="number">500</span>]          <span class="comment">// [100,200,300,400,500]</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">    <span class="built_in">console</span>.log(literal)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript"></span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<blockquote>
<p>展开运算符(ES6)，它接受一个可迭代对象并将其扩展为单个元素</p>
</blockquote>
<h2 id="Truncating-an-array"><a href="#Truncating-an-array" class="headerlink" title="Truncating an array"></a>Truncating an array</h2><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span><span class="javascript"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">    <span class="keyword">let</span> arr = [<span class="number">100</span>, <span class="number">200</span>, <span class="number">300</span>, <span class="number">400</span>, <span class="number">500</span>, <span class="number">600</span>]</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">    arr.length = <span class="number">3</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">    <span class="built_in">console</span>.log(arr)                                <span class="comment">// [100,200,300]</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">    arr.length = <span class="number">0</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">    <span class="built_in">console</span>.log(arr)                                <span class="comment">// []</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript"></span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<blockquote>
<p>length 方法不仅可以显示字符串大小，还可以将数组截断为任意大小</p>
</blockquote>
<h2 id="Smart-Replacing"><a href="#Smart-Replacing" class="headerlink" title="Smart Replacing"></a>Smart Replacing</h2><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span><span class="javascript"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">    <span class="keyword">let</span> str = <span class="string">&quot;This is potato and potato&quot;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">    <span class="built_in">console</span>.log(str.replace(<span class="regexp">/pot/</span>, <span class="string">&quot;tom&quot;</span>))          <span class="comment">// This is tomato and potato</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">    <span class="built_in">console</span>.log(str.replace(<span class="regexp">/pot/g</span>, <span class="string">&quot;tom&quot;</span>))         <span class="comment">// This is tomato and tomato</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript"></span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<blockquote>
<p>替换特定词</p>
</blockquote>
<h2 id="Numerical-Separator"><a href="#Numerical-Separator" class="headerlink" title="Numerical Separator"></a>Numerical Separator</h2><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span><span class="javascript"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">    <span class="keyword">let</span> data1 = <span class="number">10_0000</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">    <span class="keyword">let</span> data2 = <span class="number">3_0000_0000</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">    <span class="built_in">console</span>.log(data1)                              <span class="comment">// 100000</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">    <span class="built_in">console</span>.log(data2)                              <span class="comment">// 300000000</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript"></span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<blockquote>
<p>这个简单的技巧可以提高 JavaScript 大量数据的可读性</p>
</blockquote>
<h2 id="Quick-Power-Calculation"><a href="#Quick-Power-Calculation" class="headerlink" title="Quick Power Calculation"></a>Quick Power Calculation</h2><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span><span class="javascript"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">    <span class="comment">// Normal Way</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">    <span class="built_in">console</span>.log(<span class="built_in">Math</span>.pow(<span class="number">4</span>, <span class="number">5</span>))                     <span class="comment">// 1024</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">    <span class="built_in">console</span>.log(<span class="built_in">Math</span>.pow(<span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">5</span>))                     <span class="comment">// 32</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">    <span class="comment">// Quick Way</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">    <span class="built_in">console</span>.log(<span class="number">4</span> ** <span class="number">5</span>)                             <span class="comment">// 1024</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">    <span class="built_in">console</span>.log(<span class="number">2</span> ** <span class="number">5</span>)                             <span class="comment">// 32</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript"></span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<blockquote>
<p>pow() 方法来计算任何数字的幂，这个技巧将常规数学方法以快速形式计算次方</p>
</blockquote>
<h2 id="Rest-Parameter"><a href="#Rest-Parameter" class="headerlink" title="Rest Parameter"></a>Rest Parameter</h2><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span><span class="javascript"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">    <span class="function"><span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="title">sum</span>(<span class="params">...num</span>) </span>&#123;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">        <span class="keyword">let</span> cal = <span class="number">0</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">        <span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="keyword">const</span> a <span class="keyword">of</span> num) &#123;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">            cal += a</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">        &#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">        <span class="built_in">console</span>.log(cal)                            <span class="comment">// 27</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">    &#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">    sum(<span class="number">20</span>,<span class="number">7</span>)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript"></span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<blockquote>
<p>Rest Parameter 语法用于处理函数中定义中的无限数量的参数</p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p><em>！如有错误请在评论及时指出</em></p>
</blockquote>
]]></content>
